    <h1>Cheeseburger Recipe</h1>
    <h2><a href="../index.html">Home</a></h2>
    <img src="../images/cheeseburger.jpeg" width="400">
    <h4>As you may or may not have noticed, I am (oh well,
         I guess most people are) a big fan of burgers.
         This weekend I made a really good one.</h4>
    <h3>Ingredients:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>x2 100 grams beef patties</li>
        <li>sliced cheese</li>
        <li>pickled cucumbers and onion</li>
        <li>toasted brioche buns</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Steps:</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>Add a generous sprinkle of salt on both sides of the patties.</li>
        <li>Grill or fry the burger patties until prefered doneness, I went for medium.</li>
        <li>Add cheese and smear mayo on a toasted bun.</li>
        <li>Add onion and pickles.</li>
    </ol>
   
